{"id":712937,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nikon_(Liolin)","text":"Archbishop Nikon (secular name Nicholas Liolin; October 9, 1945 \u2013 September 1, 2019) was an American-Albanian bishop. He was the head of the Orthodox Church in America's Albanian Archdiocese and New England diocese. He was born New York City.\nNikon died September 1, 2019 in Southbridge, Massachusetts at the age of 73.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":92},{"uri":"Albania","surface_form":"Albanian","offset":101},{"uri":"Bishop","surface_form":"bishop","offset":110},{"uri":"Orthodox_Church_in_America","surface_form":"Orthodox Church in America","offset":141},{"uri":"Orthodox_Church_in_America_Albanian_Archdiocese","surface_form":"Albanian Archdiocese","offset":170},{"uri":"Orthodox_Church_in_America_Diocese_of_New_England","surface_form":"New England diocese","offset":195},{"uri":"New_York_City","surface_form":"New York City","offset":228},{"uri":"Southbridge%2C_Massachusetts","surface_form":"Southbridge, Massachusetts","offset":275}]}